== Kwakira neza ==
Filime yakiriwe neza n'abayireba. Isubiramo ryegeranya Rotten Tomatoes ivuga ko 83% by'abanegura umwuga bahaye filime isuzuma ryiza, naho impuzandengo ya 6.8 kuri 10. <ref>[http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/skoonheid/ Skoonheid - Rotten Tomatoes]</ref> Abenshi mu banegura bashimye imikorere ya Deon Lotz <nowiki>, Peter Bradshaw wo muri ''</nowiki> ''The Guardian'' 'yise "Igikorwa gikomeye, ariko cyihishe kandi kitoroshye"<ref>Beauty (2011) - Video Detective <nowiki>https://www.videodetective.com</nowiki> › movie › beauty-26595</ref> .  David Parkinson wo mu <nowiki><i id="mwPg">kinyamakuru Empire Magazine na</i></nowiki> we yashimye Lotz, kandi mu nyenyeri eshatu kuri eshanu zasuzumye incamake y'urubanza rwe agira ati: "Nubwo iri zina, hari imbaraga mbi kuri ubu bushakashatsi bwo gutwarwa n'uburakari<ref>Review: Beauty (2011) - Roobla <nowiki>https://roobla.com</nowiki> › beauty-skoonheid-2011-movie-rev...</ref>." 

== Ibihembo ==
''Ubwiza'' bwahawe igihembo cya Queer Palm mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2011.  Umukinnyi Deon Lotz yakiriwe bidasanzwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Zurich 2011 kubera ibikorwa bye muri iyi filime<ref>About: Beauty (2011 film) - DBpedia <nowiki>https://dbpedia.org</nowiki> › page › Beauty_(2011_film)</ref>.

